{"tid":1763160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"餐廳經理涉助被捕示威者逃脫 遭控妨礙司法公正","createTime":"2019-11-30T06:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T15:32:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"42e87fca65e8f86f7b993619c309bc22acfcbfd9","tid":1763160,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:16:38.000Z","msg":"一對男女涉嫌在本月10日於九龍塘又一城的示威活動期間，破壞商場內電表箱和閘門被截停拘查，其間一名餐廳經理，聯同其餘示威者，聲稱要營救被捕男女，涉嫌襲擊4名警員，衝突期間女疑犯成功逃脫。35歲被告韋頴恒，報稱餐廳經理，被控4項襲警及一項妨礙司法公正罪，案件今天在西九龍裁判法院提堂。裁判官將案押後至明年1月10日再訊，被告暫時毋須答辯，以待控方作進一步調查，包括翻查閉路電視紀錄和進行認人手續，被告申請保釋被拒。辯方澄清被告亦身兼餐廳股東。<br />\n<br />\n2019-11-30 14:10:04"},{"pid":"a81296b21c1329256acc9ca0b9da06c3559c5fb3","tid":1763160,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1055d705f4ee30afe70f42a91021397318cf1a45","tid":1763160,"uid":304934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba798f6ad05510cb10b9fabd8d1e836aa2ab7b8","tid":1763160,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d3e4314415827373b1a44820da06a24d9c07a3","tid":1763160,"uid":181088,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"唉搵所以咪叫靜d囉"},{"pid":"3a8749057700c81a1d589f628b4f34c79b7dc737","tid":1763160,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facbb590ea151486b6ca3