0e2f0b0d893862558b23b6","tid":1763160,"uid":26441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978fcf6c3f8668707e588e16f0080c849e5c3603","tid":1763160,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:24:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2119dc426095b0d501a0678750c20e068eb8a14f","tid":1763160,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"35歲被告韋頴恒，報稱餐廳經理，被控於本年11月10日，在九龍塘又一城商場LG層「千両」外，襲擊4名警務人員A、B、C、D，並在同一場合，襲擊和阻撓兩名正在看守犯人的警員，意圖導致兩名被捕人士逃離警方羈押。辯方澄清他身兼餐廳股東，曾留學海外直至06年回流返港發展飲食業。<br />\n<br />\n根據控方指控，本月初有市民在網上號召，呼籲示威者同月10日到又一城參與激烈的示威活動，警方因應號召到場戒備。一對男女示威者涉嫌破壞商場內大閘和電表箱，當場被警方制服拘查。被告聯同其他示威者見狀，包圍警方並向他們示敵意，被告一度大喊「救人」，並涉嫌襲擊4名警員，混亂中兩名疑犯一度逃脫，惟男疑犯最終再度被捕。控方指，被告涉嫌出拳和踢傷警員，武力程度較其他示威者高，指控嚴重，反對保釋。"},{"pid":"5d721a7d3d204b30db10349416a632cd360182dd","tid":1763160,"uid":316559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bcaa795bb4790697dc9befaa3f8eeeb2290887d","tid":1763160,"uid":6152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:28:37.000Z","msg":"唉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 餐廳係咩<br />\n我要捐錢"},{"pid":"4038b9f2c6ac73d54d43fcb97d523fbb442192c8","tid":1763160,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf89d25c4c2d46b8767fa4a29a61432e79b622d","tid":1763160,"uid":48427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\